---
layout: default
type: home
---

<h1>JSON for Pile</h1>

<h2>Using the _data/packets Jekyll Mechanism</h2>

<ul>
{% for packet_hash in site.data.packets %}
{% assign packet_name = packet_hash[0] %}
{% assign packet = packet_hash[1] %}
  <li>{{ packet_name }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>


<h2>Phenopackets in this Pile</h2>

<ul>
{% for packet in site.static_files %}
  {% if packet.path contains "static_packets/" and
        (packet.extname == '.yaml' || packet.extname == '.json') %}
  	<li>
  		<a
        target="_blank"
        href="{{site.baseurl}}{{ packet.path }}">
  			{{ packet.path }}
  		</a>
  	</li>
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
</ul>

